{"tid":1425424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我冷氣軍師決定發起『嘆冷氣！不消費！』運動！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:06:13.000Z","uid":262592,"like":86,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b04a8ff6d62466e1243c8371556efd047a72e0","tid":1425424,"uid":262592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:08:54.000Z","msg":"果日出席黃大仙罷工集會，多人到入唔到會場，咪走番入黃大仙中心囉，點知起碼成千人走哂入商場坐哂係地下！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">何其壯觀！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇番沙田集會，一樣因爲百步梯太多人，d人坐番哂入新城市！<br />\n<br />\n既然要搞不消費運動，點解唔嘆住冷氣搞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我建議大家目標去d大地產商既商場，好似8月5咁搵d靚位坐低，睇書又好，做功課又好，帶埋野食野餐又好。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總之唔好幫襯商場入面既鋪頭！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n人數夠多又唔犯法，商場實Q都冇你符。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然和理非被人叫冷氣軍師， <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地就將<span style=\"color: red;\">「嘆冷氣」</span>進行到底！</span><br />\n<br />\n第一波目標當然係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新紅基既商場</span></span> 例如沙田新城市 元朗yoho town <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二波去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">仲搵tvb做商場show既商場</span></span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲舒服過上街日曬雨淋，商場又唔敢再放黑警入黎。<br />\n<br />\n不過太古商場呢d良心商場就唔好去喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874e11e074fce247d0dd8abe8817431f9b881e16","tid":1425424,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:11:24.000Z","msg":"揀星期6日或者平日6點後開始應該好多人響應"},{"pid":"1c10c0288d1f5adaafc44edde02ad80834422aa1","tid":1425424,"uid":262592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874e11e074fce247d0dd8abe8817431f9b881e16","tid":1425424,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:11:24.000Z","msg":"揀星期6日或者平日6點後開始應該好多人響應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:13:43.000Z","msg":"剩係星期六日d地產商都死啦"},{"pid":"f7133d1fc1b835768b60958876ad954af418e69b","tid":1425424,"uid":300602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"推到有成效 <br />\n有埋本書去睇 唔消費！"},{"pid":"9b4601dfdecfce8b09067a9bdffda949aa0f1b6d","tid":1425424,"uid":262592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fbffc944e2d3e989d2efc2dd86aa444860a2c925","tid":1425424,"uid":262592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1fc2a51050690b2a25060e9d5e1b1c7344d6350e","tid":1425424,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"推啊<br />\n揀遊客區都唔錯，變相光復埋（減少大陸人）"},{"pid":"33f917f87d8d4c3ff711088a2ef7a8e2959acd56","tid":1425424,"uid":262592,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YrO5D3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4YrO5D3.jpg&h=e2fcff45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新地商場名單"},{"pid":"9c097bb5be17fe64e5f86def737c21ba591e666f","tid":1425424,"uid":262592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:21:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fed3815507ba7d023b93f624d89bdb91af122ec1","tid":1425424,"ui